rComments: Just count how many times she says UMMMM in class! She thinks a lot, but very wel dressed. This course was tough, as she didnt really use the textbook-was all based on her lectures.

I took this course when biology courses were still called BGY and not BIO, so listen up! Shes a great prof and knows what shes doing.  How to get an A... 1) GO TO CLASS, 2) Write down EVERYTHING she says 3) Memorize her lec notes 4) GO TO CLASS...Many of the final exam questions were based on what she SAID in class and whats on the lec notes!

tough class, you need to keep on top of your work. this isnt a class where u can study the night before. Professor Aarts is an excellent professor, she really knows her stuff and is pretty clear in lecture. Exams are really fair and are based only on lecture material.She can get sidetracked in office hours sometimes, but overall a great professor.
